  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Benson Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "2 Samuel 14:17",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2 Samuel 14:17",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "The word of my lord the king shall now be comfortable — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Upon reflection, she grew confident that the king’s answer would be according to her heart’s desire. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "For as an angel of God is my lord the king — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "In wisdom, justice, and goodness. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "To discern good and bad — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "To distinguish between reasonable and unreasonable petitions, and to know what is good and what evil, and understand every matter that comes before him. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Therefore the Lord thy God will be with thee — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "To direct thee to judge aright, and show mercy: or, because thou art so wise and gracious to those who in strict justice deserve punishment. God will own and stand by thee in this thy act of grace: or, God will prosper thee in thy enterprises.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "p",
        "text": "",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "br",
            "class": "",
            "text": "",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
